data.description: Welcome to this stunning home. A beautifully updated and spacious cape cod with 3 bedrooms and an additional bedroom in the basement, complete with 2 modern bathrooms. The open floor plan of the main level seamlessly combines the kitchen and dining room. The newly renovated kitchen features elegant cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances, making it a stunning focal point of the house. The fully finished basement boasts a large family room as well as an additional bedroom, bathroom, and laundry room, and all appliances are included. This home is perfect for hosting family and friends, and it underwent significant renovations in 2019 to achieve its current immaculate condition. Fresh paint and hardwood flooring give the entire space a clean, polished look. The hardwood flooring continues through all four bedrooms. The attached two-car fenced-in garage provides ample space for your vehicles and extra storage. The home also features updated insulation for added comfort, and a new furnace, central A/C, and water heater installed in 2019 ensure reliable and energy-efficient heating, cooling, and hot water.    You'll love the convenient location of this gem, situated just a short distance from public transportation, local dining, parks, shopping, and many other attractions too numerous to list. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this your new home-book your showing today!
